{"tid":294400,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"本民前梁天琦訪問加拿大國會山莊並與參議院人權委員會主席會面","createTime":"2017-06-23T02:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T10:16:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6bcb96b5474d106134d7247329cef110df0dffc7","tid":294400,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:48:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCPForum/posts/1753967771288049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCPForum%2Fposts%2F1753967771288049&d=J0RvhQqUFeYyBXbsm1e2lkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=03a56e95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCPForum/posts/1753967771288049</a><br />\n<br />\n梁天琦昨日到訪加拿大國會山莊，並請求加國對香港政治自由及人權狀況作調查。文政網將繼續遊說加國政府，以及尋求成立特別香港小組的可能性。相關會議將於下星期繼續。<br />\n<br />\n圖為梁天琦會見參議院人權委員會主席Jim Munson；<br />\n<br />\n於官方反對黨辦公室會見保守黨參議員Garnett Genuis，其為保守黨人權及宗教自由評論員；<br />\n<br />\n參觀位於渥太華之香港保衛戰參戰士兵紀念碑。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19260551_1753961441288682_4789986625618609600_n.jpg?oh=c196937f6db459aeaf931e3e3e222c64&amp;oe=59CC7C70\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19260551_1753961441288682_4789986625618609600_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dc196937f6db459aeaf931e3e3e222c64%26oe%3D59CC7C70&h=16883be8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19275207_1753961444622015_322471607095041547_n.jpg?oh=e167736af52cf62a9a2b854b7d58295c&amp;oe=59D30AB5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19275207_1753961444622015_322471607095041547_n.jpg%3Foh%3De167736af52cf62a9a2b854b7d58295c%26oe%3D59D30AB5&h=5a214ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19420386_1753961521288674_5350363369678794642_n.jpg?oh=ff1ad7862d64bf5c0228aaddcbe774ae&amp;oe=59E38C0C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum